    "31021731": {
      "title": "Influence of the pH on the synthesis of reduced graphene oxide under hydrothermal conditions",
      "abstract": "Here we describe the important role played by the pH on the morphology and structure of the reduced graphite oxide (rGO) samples obtained by hydrothermal treatment of the previously prepared GO. The nature of the resulting samples has been studied on the basis of a complete battery of experimental techniques."
